(Chapter 4 - Heat) Tj T*
(Activity 4.1) Tj T*
(Objective: Feeling hot and cold water temperature difference.) Tj T*
(Materials Required: Three bowls, cold, warm and lukewarm water.) Tj T*
(Procedure: Put left hand in cold water and right hand in warm water. Then put both in lukewarm water.) Tj T*
(Observation: Left hand feels it warm, right hand feels it cold.) Tj T*
(Discussion: Sense of touch is not reliable for measuring heat.) Tj T*
